message.entry: The linear gain must be a real scalar.
The input gain must be a real scalar.
The IIP3 must be a real scalar.
The AM/PM conversion must be a real scalar.
The lower input power limit for AM/PM conversion must be a real scalar.
The upper input power limit for AM/PM conversion must be a real scalar.
The upper input power limit for AM/PM conversion must be greater than the lower limit.
The smoothness factor for the Rapp model must be a real scalar.
The output gain must be a real scalar.
The output saturation level for the Rapp model must be a real scalar.
The AM/AM parameters for the Saleh model must be a real vector of length 2.
The AM/PM parameters for the Saleh model must be a real vector of length 2.
The AM/AM parameters for the Ghorbani model must be a real vector of length 4.
The AM/PM parameters for the Ghorbani model must be a real vector of length 4.
